      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a vehicle with great potential? This car is in rougher condition and is ready for someone who loves a hands-on fixer-upper! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical or cosmetic TLC, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the cost. Perfect for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast looking for their next rewarding challenge!",
