      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, has been maintained to the most exacting standards. Mechanically superior and aesthetically unrivaled, this motorcar offers an investment-grade driving experience for the most sophisticated collector.",
